transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Hanji sir.
Executive: Hanji mam good afternoon kaise ho aap?
Customer: Good afternoon badhiya.
Executive: Achcha sir mam jo product vagaira add hue the sab images vagaira lag gaya na?
Customer: Jo matlab kafi to maine kar liya hai thode se rehte hain wo main abhi baith ke kar hi rahi hun.
Executive: Ek minute mam.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Na kal aap shayad ek do bar phone ki thi to ek miss ho gaya tha. Hamare yaha ticket raise ho gaya.
Customer: Haan wo maine puchne ke liye kiya tha kuch to doubt maine clear kar liya tha fir apne aap hi.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai theek hai mam to.
